Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:02.57,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}昨日までの経験とか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:05.57,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}知識なんか荷物なだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:08.62,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}風はいつも通り過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:11.54,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}後に何も残さないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:14.50,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}新しい道を探せ!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:17.46,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}他人(ひと)の地図を広げるな!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:20.46,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}伏せた目を上げた時に
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:23.51,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}0(ゼロ)になるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.09,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕らは夢見てるか?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:29.35,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}未来を信じているか?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.48,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}怖いもの知らず身の程知らず
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.85,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}無鉄砲なまま
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.11,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}今僕らは夢見てるか?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:41.03,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}子供のようにまっさらに…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:47.57,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}支配された鎖は引きちぎろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:48.87,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}何もできない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.12,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ちゃんとできない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.45,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}それがどうした
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.29,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}僕らは若いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:54.58,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}何もできない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.00,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}すぐにできない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.50,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}だから僕らに可能性があるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:00.80,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}雨は止んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:02.13,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}風は止んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.59,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}見たことのない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:05.30,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}光が差すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.72,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}今が時だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:12.06,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}君は生まれ変わったBeginner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:02.57,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}到昨天为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:05.57,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}经验和知识只是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:08.62,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}风总是在掠过之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:11.54,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不留下任何痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:14.50,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}探索新的道路吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:17.46,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}会展开怎样的地图呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:20.46,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}抬起低垂的双眼时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.63,0:18:23.51,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一切将重整归零
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.09,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我们有着梦想吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:29.35,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}还如此深信着未来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.48,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知恐惧为何不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.85,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}鲁莽行事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.11,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如今我们有着梦想吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:41.03,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}将比孩童时更加沉重的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:47.57,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}支配着自己的锁链狠狠撕碎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:48.87,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不可能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.12,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}没办法做好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:51.45,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}那又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.29,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}那只是我们还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:54.58,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.00,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}无法一气呵成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:59.50,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}正因如此我们还有着可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:00.80,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}雨停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:02.13,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}风停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.59,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}前所未见的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:05.30,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}照耀着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.72,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}现在正是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:12.06,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}你已脱胎换骨了!
