Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:53.56,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}真実は伝わるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.14,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}時間の川に託した
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.69,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}その光のメッセージ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:01.48,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}受け取る者は誰だい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.65,0:20:03.82,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}人は生まれて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.98,0:20:06.28,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}人は死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:11.45,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}肉体は滅びるよ
