Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理第9位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速报只是中途的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会发生什么变化谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.25,0:00:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究生竟然冲到第9位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 你就坦率地高兴点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究生进入速报排名可是很少见的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互相加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.97,0:00:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是强者 好从容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2位吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.94,0:00:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴躁了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第2位也是非常好的名次了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.03,0:00:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却完全不满足
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对 袭名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了哦 小智惠的海报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:00:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么要做出那么阴沉的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话 就应该更加闪耀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 再闪耀一些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 看啊 看啊 看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临近总选举的握手会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉丝们兴致也很高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家可不要输给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说总选举前的握手会对之后的好评增长影响很大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听到这些话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松放松
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总选举就是节日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不尽兴的话就浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kojiharu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我投票给佐江了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 成员给成员投票是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是谢谢你了 小惠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到鼓舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐江
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才忘记说了 这次77期也会分为每人一队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:03:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每人一队?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们全体集合起来也比不上一个袭名成员的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真琴的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是凪沙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有这么多人等着和我握手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是连日以来的改革运动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及研究生演唱会显示出的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 那条队伍好厉害哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 那是你的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.71,0:04:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 简直是袭名成员的水平了 智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时此刻 心被刺痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 是我啊 还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的握手会上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 逗你的 今天是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我已经决定支持你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对会让你进入选拔组的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:04:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一位请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次 一定要记得我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很可爱 凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总选举 我也会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 为什么会为了我加油呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为凪沙也很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 AKB审判让我迷上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 但是那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你才能成为新的00先驱者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚公开的I GIRL NOODLE的广告太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I GIRL NOODLE的广告?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 待机也很紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 但是所有的工作中 我最喜欢握手会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你之前还被吓得发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 友歌坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚 楚方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁哭捏捏的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是屁股捏捏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经交换队伍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人为什么可以变得坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭泣也好 叫喊也好 摔倒也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有值得信任的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 把即将到来的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变为成功的先例
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有值得信任的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I GIRL NOODLE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然拍广告 太狡猾了 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的镜头 那个背影不是智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听说过要拍摄I GIRL NOODLE食品的广告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对方擅自使用了审判时流出的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,允许发生这样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们进行的是非法的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不经许可使用了我们的影像也无法申诉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 回到队伍里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉丝们并不了解那个广告的内幕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么气呼呼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是楚方拍了广告的话 一定很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 已经睡了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很累吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加握手会的人数也是我们的一倍以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也差不多要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总选举 到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才加姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已经这个时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin和Yukirin也在那边练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都睡不着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为太兴奋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是总选举嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:09:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱 去安慰一下怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想那样做的话 光一定不会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我们是劲敌啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后我们两个要是能在总选举的舞台上竞争就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱那个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会止步于第二的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要超越第13代前田敦子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会夺得第一的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不这么做的话就没法给彼方做榜样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要继续做那孩子所憧憬的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我唯一能为本应成为Takamina的那孩子所做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.41,0:09:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论谁胜谁负都愿赌服输哦 优子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一定会是我赢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.99,0:10:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的你是那么遥远的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了总选举
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家保持着各种各样的思绪在战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究生她们所引发的Center Nova现象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了总选举 大家互相展开竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经非常接近前代啊酱的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这或许就是解开Center Nova的消失之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解救她们的唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才加姐和优子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在为了总选举而拼命努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已经拿到前十了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而却…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.96,0:11:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼方一钻进被窝肯定三秒内就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰她睡觉的话 会很不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在给Fan们写回信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 全都是手写的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以看一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}你好～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}感谢你一直以来的支持!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}在下就是岸田美森～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}收到你的来信真的好开心啊。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}特别是想到手绘T恤的事 情不自禁地就笑起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}我觉得前几天握手会时穿的那件黄色T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}真的超适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}在新的学校有交到新朋友吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}在完全陌生的地方与素昧平生的人们一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}一开始真的很艰难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}但是你的话肯定没问题的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}握手会时你特地给我看的那张有笑容的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上至握手会 下到服装
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然都这么详细地记住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}你好～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}谢谢你的来信啦! 我是岸田美森～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}腱鞘炎现在康复了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}听说最近依然阵阵作痛真的好担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}就算是这个时期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}也要特意写几封信给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}真的真的好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}谢谢你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}我觉得办公类的工作也蛮辛苦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}别太勉强自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}有空要好好休息才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30\c&H282A2C&\3c&H9EBDDA&}健康才是人生最大的本钱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森姐意外的是努力家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住跟Fan们所相遇的每一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不需要努力什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:12:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 我也是那些追随我的Fan们的Fan啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fan的Fan吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把不曾在前排出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.22,0:12:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直像在影子中的我找到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不吝啬地将爱给予了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说着「喜欢我」的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是怀着要为大家投支持的一票的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来写这些信的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真琴怎么还穿着睡衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为一直都是休息日的今天突然变成自主练习了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回一定要倒头就睡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡到心满意足为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 楚方也要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:13:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直睡下去 睡到心满意足为止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}今天是猫型睡衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}总选举已经近在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:03.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么悠闲真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们没什么关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速报也没入围嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然最开始宣布总选举时很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是跟非前十确实没什么关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总选举给予所有人的机会是平等的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我跟彼方去自主练习了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森姐真的很积极呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也是努力家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我也来练习好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚方也要入围选拔!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒 叽歪佛祖也来加入练习练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要睡觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}一直睡下去 睡到满意为止!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 必须要叫上智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理的话 一大早就出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许久不见了 安永
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的没想到智惠理大小姐会主动联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐因为想加入AKB0048的事被父亲所反对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而离家出走之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安永无时无刻不在担心着…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I GIRL NOODLE的广告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I GIRL食品是隶属于Zodiac的企业
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 对AKB审判时 Zodiac的摄影机也在场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事 安永
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 CEO有留言给您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 好想见你 Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你离家已经一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我最初想把你带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你身边的偶像光芒却渐渐闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不再反对你加入AKB0048了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 不 整个Zodiac企业会全力支持园智惠理的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 那些solo业务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些广告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是因为我的实力而看上我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那次审判也是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才让大家陷入危险之中的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请转告我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会让他随心所欲的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃我的梦想 也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就看她自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我正在为总选举上要表演的迷你演唱会练习
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和凪沙你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不喜欢总选举
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌为了踢出伙伴从而上位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而用一些肮脏的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肮脏的手段?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 阿守 还没好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 信号不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是AKB总选举的大日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 守 你投给谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 当然是铃子小姐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只投给了铃子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那是当然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有图像了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了 彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}星历
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}0048年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}新单曲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}选拔总选举
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs30}向着银河誓约的决胜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉和平时完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara就像火焰般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊燃烧 闪耀发光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是竞争心态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.77,0:18:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竞争心态?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先代啊酱和翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说是七代目麻里子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在啊酱之前的Center可是翼小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 原来翼小姐之前当过Center Nova啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 没当过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在啊酱袭名之前的总选举中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被选中当过一次Center而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当不了Center Nova的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闲话就谈到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种气压
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉丝们今天好像在向我们挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 应该说是众人一心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.92,0:19:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总选举
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 研究生们的Kirara光芒不够闪耀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加强点照明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被会场的氛围给震住了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 总算恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.53,0:20:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到这一刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0048年度选拔总选举
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司仪就由我三代目德三担任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉丝们的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理和凪沙到底谁会排在前面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}0048年度选拔总选举
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}选拔名单就要公布了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.85,0:21:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 为了防止黑幕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请允许我公布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在公布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第十位是
