Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第75期研究生 岸田美森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美森
